<!doctype html>
<html lang="de">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>__EVENT_NAME__ Setup</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: dark;
        --bg-a: #09111b;
        --bg-b: #071623;
        --accent: #4fd1e2;
        --accent-strong: #9df3ff;
        --panel: rgba(11, 18, 29, 0.92);
        --border: rgba(135, 186, 229, 0.2);
        --text: rgba(246, 250, 255, 0.96);
        --muted: rgba(203, 217, 231, 0.72);
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        padding: 24px;
        font-family: "Trebuchet MS", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(79, 209, 226, 0.16), transparent 32%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-a), var(--bg-b));
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .panel {
        width: min(100%, 420px);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: var(--panel);
        padding: 28px 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      }

      .eyebrow {
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.22em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        line-height: 1.08;
      }

      p {
        margin: 14px 0 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-flex;
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 22px;
        padding: 15px 18px;
        border: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
        color: #041018;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .fallback {
        margin-top: 18px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      code {
        color: var(--accent-strong);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="panel">
      <div class="eyebrow">RaveBerg</div>
      <h1>WLAN einrichten</h1>
      <p>Bitte WLAN fuer das Event auswaehlen. Du wirst jetzt direkt zur lokalen Setup-Oberflaeche weitergeleitet.</p>
      <form id="portal-form" method="get" action="$authaction">
        <input type="hidden" name="tok" value="$tok" />
        <input type="hidden" name="redir" value="__PORTAL_URL__" />
        <button class="button" type="submit">WLAN einrichten</button>
      </form>
      <p class="fallback">Falls sich nichts oeffnet: <code>__FALLBACK_URL__</code></p>
    </main>
    <script>
      window.setTimeout(function () {
        var form = document.getElementById('portal-form');
        if (form) form.submit();
      }, 1200);
    </script>
  </body>
  </html>
